                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textView19"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="“Smart College Bus System” is a system which allows the student to keep track of the bus in the morning and the student can also communicate with the driver through notifications…!!!  The system basically solves the real-life problem. It helps students to have a track of their bus so that they can be regular to college, also includes authentications like if the student has paid the bus fee or not and other scenarios. It also allows the student to send notifications from his phone like “Will be there in a minute” and many other notifications so that the driver will know that a student is late for the bus. The system also allows the driver to keep a track of number of students entering from a particular stop, hence allowing the driver also to send notification to the student, if he/she is missing in the bus.  The anticipated end result is to provide a bug free, user friendly, efficient software to those students who travel by college bus on day-to-day basis, which helps the student know where bus is and the student being ready on time, not being late for the bus. "
